<template>
  <Card class="border">
    <template #title>Daily Targets</template>
    <template #subtitle>All Daily Targets reached in %</template>
    <template #content>
      <Knob v-model="value" class="knob" :size="150" readonly />
    </template>
  </Card>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  data() {
    return {
      value: 70,
    };
  },
};
</script>

<style scoped>
.border {
  border-top: 8px solid var(--pink);
}

.knob svg {
  margin: auto;
  display: block;
}
</style>
